#!/bin/bash
# Gemini Pro Agent - High capability tier for Gastown
# Uses gemini-2.5-pro for complex tasks requiring deep reasoning
#
# Best for:
# - Complex architectural decisions
# - Large codebase analysis (1M token context)
# - Debugging intricate issues
